msgid ""
"Show your gratitude: Think of a Free Software project you appreciate and "
"reach out to the maintainers. Say thank you using our <a "
"href=\"https://sharepic.fsfe.org/#ilovefs\">sharepic</a>, <a "
"href=\"/contribute/spreadtheword#ilovefs\">stickers, balloons</a>, <a "
"href=\"/activities/ilovefs/artwork/artwork.html\">artwork</a>, or <a "
"href=\"/order/order.html\">merchandise </a>for #ilovefs."
msgstr ""
"Kom in actie: spreken is zilver, bijdragen is goud! Help een Vrije "
"Software-project door te doneren, te vertalen of haar gebruikers te "
"helpen. U kunt ook ons werk steunen door <a href=\"/donate/donate.html\">aan "
"de FSFE te doneren.</a>"
